  "instructions": [
    "heat the coconut oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "add the ground cumin, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "add the uruguayan ground beef and cook until browned, breaking it up with a spoon as it cooks.",
    "add the dashi-extract and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "stir in the thai chilli jam and cook for 1 minute.",
    "warm the pandan leaf wraps by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20 seconds.",
    "assemble the wraps by spooning the beef mixture onto the center of each wrap and topping with chopped cilantro and a dollop of ayurvedic ghee.",
    "serve immediately and enjoy!"
